    <h2>Configuration</h2>
    <p>RugbyClaw works immediately after install using proxy mode (50 requests/day). For unlimited requests, add your own free <a href="https://api-sports.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">API-Sports key</a>:</p>
    <pre><code>rugbyclaw config</code></pre>

    <h2>Supported Leagues</h2>
    <p>RugbyClaw supports <strong>13 leagues</strong> including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Club:</strong> Top 14, Pro D2, Premiership, URC, Super Rugby Pacific</li>
        <li><strong>European:</strong> Champions Cup, Challenge Cup</li>
        <li><strong>International:</strong> Six Nations, Women's Six Nations, Rugby Championship</li>
        <li><strong>Regional:</strong> Currie Cup, NPC, MLR</li>
        <li><strong>World Cup</strong></li>
    </ul>
